      "text": [
        " لَا تَرِثُ النِّسَاءُ مِنْ عَقَارِ الْأَرْضِ شَيْئاً ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Jameel, from Zurara and Muhammad Bin Muslim, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Ja’far<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The women do not inherit anything from realty of the land’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "4. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘Umayr from Jamil from Zurarah and Muhammad ibn Muslim who has narrated the following: “Abu Ja‘far, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Women do not inherit from the real property or land anything.’” "
        ]
      }
